The '''IC3''' certification ([[Internet]] Core Competency Certification) is a global [[benchmarking|benchmark]] for basic [[computer literacy]], including [[operating system]]s, [[hardware (computer)|hardware]], [[software]], and [[computer network|networks]].<ref name="totalsem">{{cite web|url=http://www.totalsem.com/blog/ic3-certification-career/|title=Total Seminars - Best selling books plus practice exams for A+, Network+, and IC3 certification|publisher=totalsem.com|accessdate=2015-11-02}}</ref> The [[test (assessment)|test]] is administered by Certiport®.

