The '''University Grants Commission Act, 1956'''<ref>{{cite web|title=UGC Act-1956|url=http://mhrd.gov.in/sites/upload_files/mhrd/files/upload_document/ugc_act.pdf|website=mhrd.gov.in/|publisher=Secretary, University Grants Commission|accessdate=1 February 2016}}</ref> is an [[Act of Parliament|Act]] of the [[Parliament of India]].<ref name="University Grants Commission (India) -">{{cite web|url=http://www.ugc.ac.in/oldpdf/ugc_act.pdf|title=The University Grants Commission Act, 1956 (As modified up to the 20th December, 1985) and Rules & Regulations under the Act|publisher=[[University Grants Commission (India)]]|accessdate=4 January 2015}}</ref> The Act is sometimes referred to as "the UGC Act".<ref name="The Hindu - 3 June 2012 - UGC defers plan to allow entry of foreign varsities">{{cite news|url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/ugc-defers-plan-to-allow-entry-of-foreign-varsities/article3483922.ece|title=UGC defers plan to allow entry of foreign varsities|last=Dhar|first=Aarti|date=3 June 2012|work=[[The Hindu]]|publisher=[[The Hindu Group]]|accessdate=4 January 2015}}</ref>

